headline: Why Generac (GNRC) Stock Is Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of power generation products company Generac (NYSE:GNRC) fell 2.3% in the morning session after investment firm Canaccord Genuity lowered its price target on the stock, pointing to a mild hurricane season and fewer power outages.
